    <string name="settings_changelog_title">View changelog</string>
    <string name="settings_changelog_body">Welcome to Motoko v1.0!\n\nThis is the initial release of Motoko, your personal finance manager designed to help you take control of your money.\n\n- Dashboard: Track your income, expenses, and balance at a glance. View your latest transactions and monitor your budget with ease.\n- History: Browse, search, and filter past transactions by time, category, and type.\n- Subscriptions: Keep track of your monthly and annual subscriptions with automatic billing period totals.\n- Categories: Organize your transactions by customizable categories with unique icons.\n- Wallets: Manage multiple wallets (Cash, Debit Card, Savings) to see where your money is stored.\n- Accounts: Separate your finances across different accounts (Personal, Work, Joint) with full transaction isolation.\n- Settings: Customize your experience with theme options, font styles, text size, app lock, and data import/export.\n- Privacy: Enable privacy mode to hide sensitive amounts, or lock the app behind biometric authentication.\n- Receipts: Attach receipt images to any transaction for easy record-keeping.\n\nMotoko is built by Ixeken Studios. All your data stays on your device — we don\'t track, we don\'t store, we don\'t know.</string>
