    <string name="settings_privacy_dialog_title">Privacy</string>
    <string name="settings_privacy_dialog_body">At Ixeken Studios, your privacy is our priority.\n\nAll your financial data, transactions, accounts, subscriptions, and receipts are stored exclusively on your device. Ixeken Studios has no access to your data, no way to know how you use the app, and no way to know if you even use the app at all.\n\nThe app does not send any personal or financial data over the internet. There is no analytics, crash reporting, or telemetry. In fact, checking for updates is the only feature in the entire app that uses internet access, and it only runs if you explicitly trigger it or enable automatic checks on startup.\n\nOptionally, if you enable the \"Check for updates\" feature, the app will make a single request to GitHub Releases to check your current version against the latest available version. No personal information is sent — only a public version identifier. This feature is entirely optional and disabled by default.\n\nWhen you export your data, the exported file is in your full control. You are solely responsible for handling, storing, and sharing that exported data.</string>

